article.headline: Thomas scores 22 as Montana knocks off Northern Arizona 90-47
article.description: — Dischon Thomas scored 22 points as Montana beat Northern Arizona 90-47 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Thomas scores 22 as Montana knocks off Northern Arizona 90-47
article.story: MISSOULA, Mont. -- — Dischon Thomas scored 22 points as Montana beat Northern Arizona 90-47 on Saturday night. Thomas shot 8 for 14, including 5 for 8 from beyond the arc for the Grizzlies (11-6, 2-2 Big Sky Conference). Aanen Moody scored 19 points while going 7 of 12 (5 for 7 from 3-point range). Te'Jon Sawyer finished 5 of 8 from the floor to finish with 10 points. The Lumberjacks (7-10, 0-3) were led by Carson Basham, who recorded 14 points, six rebounds and three blocks. Oakland Fort added eight points for Northern Arizona. In addition, Rockwell Reynolds finished with six points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
